data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Discover your dream home in the active 55+ community of Highland Lakes! This cozy 2 bed, 2 bath home offers 1546 sq. ft. of inviting space. Enjoy a well-equipped kitchen, spacious living area, and a sun-kissed Florida room overlooking a peaceful backyard with a patio. Highland Lakes provides a vibrant lifestyle with pools, tennis, bocce ball, shuffleboard courts, a fitness center, a workshop, and RV parking. Dive into endless activities! Book your tour today and embrace the Highland Lakes charm.
